<section class="ss-demo-page">
  <div class="ss-demo-hero">
    <span class="ss-demo-hero__pill">Public Demo</span>
    <h1>Explore a live private merch store before building yours.</h1>
    <p>Preview the store, products, dashboard, and admin experience. This demo uses real storefront pages, but checkout and admin actions are locked.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="ss-demo-grid">
    <article class="ss-demo-card">
      <div class="ss-demo-card__top">
        <div class="ss-demo-logo">R</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Raptors Demo Store</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>A sample team storefront showing how customers browse products, change options, and view a private collection.</p>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__meta">
        <span>Team store</span><span>Live products</span><span>Checkout locked</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__actions">
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--dark" href="/collections/raptors-3978?demo=true">View Store</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--light" href="/pages/demo-dashboard?store=raptors-3978&demo=true">View Dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ss-demo-card">
      <div class="ss-demo-card__top">
        <div class="ss-demo-logo">A</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Admin Preview</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>See the kind of tools a storefront admin gets: product management, sharing, QR/link actions, and store status.</p>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__meta">
        <span>Dashboard</span><span>Admin tools</span><span>Actions disabled</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__actions">
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--gold" href="/pages/demo-dashboard?store=raptors-3978&demo=true">Open Preview</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--light" href="/pages/request-storefront-form">Create Store</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ss-demo-card">
      <div class="ss-demo-card__top">
        <div class="ss-demo-logo">+</div>
        <div>
          <h3>More Stores Later</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>This demo library is built so more high-quality stores can be added over time without changing the customer-facing flow.</p>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__meta">
        <span>Expandable</span><span>Easy to maintain</span><span>Real examples</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ss-demo-card__actions">
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--dark" href="/pages/request-storefront-form">Start Yours</a>
        <a class="ss-demo-btn ss-demo-btn--light" href="/pages/how-it-works">How It Works</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "SS Demo Page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "SS Demo Page" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
